@node usage "usage"
                                 @{b}Usage@{ub}
 
i wrote aPersonal to try out PortacallGUInterface.

new
---
no comment..


add/edit  (to edit use add icon on any entry)
--------
1.start aPersonal
2.mouse click in first name & do enter a first name than (hit enter)to go next input
3.continue until Comment input than hit enter again.
4.if you think all correct click on right add icon.
5.ready for next index no..


stat
----
watches the memmory & data movements..(reports data/memmory spaces) 


Search (click Find icon then input first/last name hit return key & click go button )
------
dont just click in Search input instead click the find icon than you can search.

why dont i just use search & go? because i have forgoton to enable
function so i could not compile again instead use icon first but if you realy
want to use search & go email as I'll see what i can do.

del
---
goto any entry click del..

load/save 
---------
one loads & one saves
  


[<] left/cancel button

[>] right/ik button

thats all about it..


to exit click x button (bottom right)
@endnode

